annotationA: Gamma-glutamylcyclotransferase; Catalyzes the cleavage of glutathione into 5-oxo-L- proline and a Cys-Gly dipeptide. Acts specifically on glutathione, but not on other gamma-glutamyl peptides
annotationB: Glutathione peroxidase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: response to oxidative stress; oxidation-reduction process; multicellular organism reproduction
